<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07944</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE PROTECTION AND CONSERVATION OF UNDERWATER CULTURAL HERITAGE IN PHILIPPINE WATERS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Intends to supplement existing laws as regards to “cultural properties” under R.A. No.4846 (Cultural Properties Preservation and Protection Act); P.D. No.374 (Amends R.A. No.4846); R.A.No.8492 (National Museum Act); and R.A. No.10066 (National Cultural Heritage Act).
Aims therefore to establish comprehensive underwater cultural heritage preservation, protection, management, and monitoring mechanism by creating regulatory framework particularly:  regulations on excavation and exploration, the creation of a registry of items and/or sites to be protected, prohibition of certain harmful activities, a reward system for verified reports and imposition of sanction/penalties for violations.       
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>VARGAS, ALFRED D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-07-23</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-08-08)</td><td>2. Sangcopan (000 2018-10-10)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON BASIC EDUCATION AND CULTURE ON 2018-08-01</td></tr></table>